description:
I've teamed up with Pause and Beef to take on Ruins Of The MindCrackers, a CTM map featuring many of the builds of the MindCrack server. The goal is to find colored wool blocks in chests scattered around the map, and place these on the victory monument.

VintageBeef: http://www.youtube.com/user/VintageBeef

Map Name: Ruins Of The MindCrackers
Created By: Joelx1000
